proof:
theorem ℂofwoΔ (x : Η0Ja) (hx : IJ x oVΟ) : x = GnΑ0 ∨ x = gfΧ ∨ x = oVΟ := by

    have h₃ : Θ7Κr (Θ7Κr GnΑ0) = ΚxΝ x c := hc
    have h₄ : x = GnΑ0 ∨ x = gfΧ ∨ x = oVΟ := by
      -- Perform case analysis on x
      cases x with
      | GnΑ0 =>
        -- Case x = GnΑ0
        exact Or.inl rfl
      | Θ7Κr x' =>
        -- Case x = Θ7Κr x'
        have h₅ : Θ7Κr (Θ7Κr GnΑ0) = ΚxΝ (Θ7Κr x') c := by simpa using h₃
        have h₆ : ΚxΝ (Θ7Κr x') c = Θ7Κr (ΚxΝ (Θ7Κr x') c) := by
          rw [Qγx1dtΨo]
